#title Code coverage and testing
#author Arnaud Bailly

This chapter shall contains  information regarding *code coverage*
measures. It presently contains:
 - a [[control-flow.muse][technical]] introduction to control flow and basic blocks,
 - a [[coverage-sample.muse][quick review]] of some major control-flow based coverage metrics,
 - an article on the relationship between [[tdd-coverage.muse][TDD and Coverage]] metrics,
 - an [[scala-coverage.muse][overview]] of using Patchwork with Scala.